* 500-stage CMOS inverter chain (no subcircuits) using BSIM4 models
.options acct
.options num_threads=8
VDD vdd 0 1.0
*VIN n0 0 PULSE (0 1.0 0 10p 10p 2n 4n)
VIN n0 0 1
Cload n500 0 1f

* Models
.model nmos nmos (level=14 version=4.8.2)
.model pmos pmos (level=14 version=4.8.2)

* Added: series resistor between each inverter and global VDD


* Inverters expanded inline: Mp=PMOS pull-up, Mn=NMOS pull-down
* Each stage i uses local supply node vddi, with Rvddi from global vdd to vddi
Rvdd1 vdd vdd1 1k
Mp1 n1 n0 vdd1 vdd1 pmos W=1u L=45n
Mn1 n1 n0 0 0 nmos W=0.5u L=45n
Rvdd2 vdd vdd2 1k
Mp2 n2 n1 vdd2 vdd2 pmos W=1u L=45n
Mn2 n2 n1 0 0 nmos W=0.5u L=45n
Rvdd3 vdd vdd3 1k
